<?xml version="1.0" encoding="ASCII"?>
<caldef:CalDefinitionFile xmlns:caldef="http://www.caltools.gm.com/caldef" Description="This caldef contains calibrations pertient to the GIS-641 (Global B CSM Radio Component Diagnostic Specification) ">
  <CalDefFileVersion>18</CalDefFileVersion>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>1</Version>
    <Date>5/24/2016</Date>
    <Description>Inital release of this caldef file.</Description>
    <Author>David Bonello</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>2</Version>
    <Date>9/15/2016</Date>
    <Description>Deleted the following three calibrations from this caldef file since there were duplicate calibrations for these three calibrations already in this caldef file: 1.) DTC_MASK_U3003_16(CalID: _YorpMB0NEeaksf3dHPIIEA), 2.) DTC_MASK_U3003_17 (CalID: _XNPMoB0SEeaksf3dHPIIEA), and DTC_MASK_B19B1_50 (CalID: _Aco-wCGpEeaY4JYlyGk5Lw).</Description>
    <Author>Ginnard Kimbrough</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>3</Version>
    <Date>11/18/2016</Date>
    <Description> Within the GIS641_DiagnosticCalDef_GlobalB.caldef file made the following updates for RTC CR#:1248683: Updated the default value of the DTC_MASK_U240B_00 calibration from a value of True to False. Added the following eight new DTC_MASK calibrations: 1.) DTC_MASK_U3000_56, 2.) DTC_MASK_U1967_81, 3.) DTC_MASK_U1967_84, 4.) DTC_MASK_U1967_85, 5.) DTC_MASK_U1967_89, 6.) DTC_MASK_B1784_12, 7.) DTC_MASK_B1869_86, and 8.) DTC_MASK_B1869_4A. Renamed the DTV_MASK_U3000_53 calibration to DTC_MASK_U3000_53 to correct a typo issue with the way this calibration was initially named. Also, added usage type (MID, HIGH) that was also missing for this DTC_MASK_U3000_53 calibration. And, updated the default value for the DTC_MASK_U3000_53 from a value of False to True. Updated the default value of the DTC_MASK_U0156_00 calibration from a value of False to True. Renamed the DTC_MASK_B174E_11 calibration to DTC_MASK_B1784_11. Renamed the DTC_MASK_B174E_13 calibration to DTC_MASK_B1784_13. Renamed the DTC_MASK_B1981_52 calibration to DTC_MASK_B1964_52. Updated the calibration description for the following four calibrations: 1.) DTC_MASK_U3000_4A, 2.) DTC_MASK_U1967_00, 3.) DTC_MASK_B1964_00, and 4.) DTC_MASK_B1869_82 calibration to reflect the latest description in the latest GIS-641. Deleted the following three calibrations confirmed no longer to be needed and to correspond o the what is reflected in the latest GIS-641 : 1.) DTC_MASH_B1A2B_84, 2.) DTC_MASK_B1A2B_85, and 3.) DTC_MASK_B1A2B_89.</Description>
    <Author>David Bonello</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>4</Version>
    <Date>1/26/2017</Date>
    <Description>Within the GIS641_DiagnosticCalDef_GlobalB.caldef file, changed the name of the DTC_MASK_U0077_00 DTC mask calibration to DTC_MASK_U007B_00.</Description>
    <Author>David Bonello</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>5</Version>
    <Date>6/13/2017</Date>
    <Description>Within GIS641_DiagnosticCalDef_GlobalB.caldef file made the following updates: 1.) RUNNING_RESET default value changed from 0 to 5.  2.) VEHICLE_LOGISTICS_MODE default value changed from false to true. 3.)  Deleted the following calibrations since they have been removed from the current Global B release cadence 133: DTC_MASK_U1967_00, DTC_MASK_U1967_81, DTC_MASK_U1967_84, DTC_MASK_U1967_85, DTC_MASK_U1967_89, DTC_MASK_U007B_00, DTC_MASK_U240B_00, DTC_MASK_U1967_89, DTC_MASK_B1034_11, DTC_MASK_B1034_12, DTC_MASK_B1034_13, DTC_MASK_B1033_11, DTC_MASK_B1033_12, DTC_MASK_B1033_13, DTC_MASK_B1032_11, DTC_MASK_B1032_12, DTC_MASK_B1032_13, DTC_MASK_B1031_11, DTC_MASK_B1031_12, DTC_MASK_B1031_13, DTC_MASK_B1784_01, DTC_MASK_B1784_02, DTC_MASK_B1784_04, DTC_MASK_B1964_52, DTC_MASK_B198E_01, DTC_MASK_B15AF_02, DTC_MASK_B15AF_04, DTC_MASK_B15B0_02, and DTC_MASK_B15B0_04. 4.) Add the following new calibrations to support new Global B DTC reflected in  the current Global B release cadence 133:  DTC_MASK_B1A2B_84, DTC_MASK_B1A2B_85, and DTC_MASK_B1A2B_89, DTC_MASK_U0422_00, DTC_MASK_U0447_00, DTC_MASK_B198E_12, DTC_MASK_B15AF_11, DTC_MASK_B15AF_13, DTC_MASK_B15B0_11, DTC_MASK_B15B0_13, DTC_MASK_U300D_23, and DTC_MASK_U300D_24 to  support current latest Global B Cadence 133. 5.) DTC_MASK_U0156_00, DTC_MASK_B13A7_11, and DTC_MASK_B13A7_13 default values changed from true to false. 6.) The function of the B1618_13 DTC changed from Coaxial Antenna XM Signal &#x2013; Circuit Open ($13) to Voice Recognition Audio Signal Circuit Open as a result the calibration description of the DTC_MASK_B1618_13 calibration was updated accordingly to match. 7.) The function of the B1784_11 DTC changed from Coaxial Antenna XM Signal &#x2013; Circuit Short to Ground ($11) to Coaxial Antenna GPS Signal Circuit Short To Ground DTC_MASK_B1784_11 was updated accordingly to match. 8.) Updated the calibration description for the DTC_MASK_B1784_12 from DTC $B1784_12 - COAXIAL ANTENNA GPS SIGNAL CIRCUIT SHORT TO BATTE to Coaxial Antenna GPS Signal Circuit Short To Battery. 9.) Updated the calibration description for the DTC_MASK_B1784_13 from Coaxial Antenna XM Signal &#x2013; Circuit Open ($13). This sub type is used for failures, where the control module determines an open circuit via lack of bias voltage, low current flow, no change in the state of an input in response to an output, etc. to Coaxial Antenna GPS Signal Circuit Open. 10.) Updated the calibration description for the DTC_MASK_B1964_00 from DTC B1964_00 &#x2013; RADIO &#x2013; SYSTEM PRORGRAMMING FAILURE to DTC B1964_00 &#x2013; USB D (+) Serial Data General Failure Condition. 11.) Updated the calibration description for the DTC_MASK_B1965_00 from USB D (+) Serial Data - No Sub Type Information to USB D (+) Serial Data 2 General Failure Condition. 12.) The function of the B1869_29 DTC changed, and as a result the calibration description of the DTC_MASK_B1869_29 was updated accordingly to match. 13.) Changed the name of the DTC_MASK_U0198_00 calibration to DTC_MASK_U0198_00_GlobalB. Changed the name of this calibration needed for Global B too to maintain calibration name uniqueness from the existing DTC_MASK_U0198_00 calibration already being used for Global A., 14.) Changed the name of the DTC_MASK_U0196_00 calibration to DTC_MASK_U0196_00_GlobalB. Changed the name of this calibration needed for Global B too to maintain calibration name uniqueness from the existing DTC_MASK_U0196_00_GlobalB calibration already being used for Global A and  15.) Updated the usage field for all of the calibrations within this CalDef file to support the new &quot;Global A/B&quot; categorization in the CalDef tool.</Description>
    <Author>David Bonello</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>6</Version>
    <Date>1/11/2018</Date>
    <Description></Description>
    <Author>Dave Bonello</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>7</Version>
    <Date>1/24/2018</Date>
    <Description>Made the following DTC updates per CR#: 1568185 to align with DOORs CSM DTC updates made in Release Cadence 138 : Add the following twenty new DTC enable mask calibrations per CR#: 1568185 (Release Cadence  138): 1.) DTC_MASK_B1A62_82, 2.) DTC_MASK_B1A62_86, 3.) DTC_MASK_B1A62_4A,  4.) DTC_MASK_B1236_11, 5..)  DTC_MASK_B1236_13, 6.) DTC_MASK_U1967_00,                                                7.) DTC_MASK_U1967_81, 8.) DTC_MASK_U1967_84, 9.) DTC_MASK_U1967_85, 10.) DTC_MASK_U1967_89,  11.) DTC_MASK__B1B19_00,                                               12.) DTC_MASK_U1133_00, 13.) DTC_MASK_U020C_00,                                               14.) DTC_MASK_B13ED_11, 15.) DTC_MASK_B13ED_13,                                              16.) DTC_MASK_U007B_00, 17.) DTC_MASK_U196E_00,                                               18.) DTC_MASK_U196E_84, 19.) DTC_MASK_U196E_85, and                                        20.) DTC_MASK_U196E_89. Also, deleted the following nine DTC enable mask calibrations since these DTCs are no longer required to be supported: 1.) DTC_MASK_B1869_29 (note: handled by new enable mask DTC_MASK_B1A62_29), 2.) DTC_MASK_B1869_82 (note: handled by new enable mask DTC_MASK_B1A62_82), 3.) DTC_MASK_B1869_86 (note: handled by new enable mask DTC_MASK_B1A62_86), 4.) DTC_MASK_B1869_4A  (note: handled by new enable mask DTC_MASK_B1A62_4A), 5.) DTC_MASK_B198E_11  (note: handled by new enable mask DTC_MASK_B1236_11), 6.) DTC_MASK_B198E_13 (note: handled by new enable mask DTC_MASK_B1236_13) , 7.) DTC_MASK_B198E_12 (note: being deleted and no replacement required) , 8.)  DTC_MASK_B15B0_11 (note: handled instead by existing enable mask DTC_MASK_B15AF_11), and 9.) DTC_MASK_B15B0_13 (note: handled instead by existing enable mask DTC_MASK_B15AF_13).  Also per CR#s:  1425609 and 1499677, added the following two new DTC enable mask calibrations to support these DTCs being moved from the CGM to the CSM: 1.) DTC_MASK_U0140_00 and 2.) DTC_MASK_U1611_00. Also, deleted DTC_MASK_U300D_24 since this DTC for Ignition Switch H/W Input does not need to be supported by the CSM. Deleted existing DTC enable mask DTC_MASK_U0186_00, and replacing with a new enable mask called DTC_MASK_U0186_00_GlobalB with a different CalID to have a uniquely different calibration name from the existing DTC_MASK_U0186_00 enable mask calibration already in the GIS621_DiagnosticCalDef_GlobalA.caldef.</Description>
    <Author>Dave Bonello</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>8</Version>
    <Date>1/26/2018</Date>
    <Description>Documentation update only to just show a record in change history version 8 of this caldef of the following three DTC enable mask calibrations being previously removed: 1.) DTC_MASK_B1A2B_84, 2.) DTC_MASK_B1A2B_85, and 3.) DTC_MASK_B1A2B_89. Note, this was previously done in change history version 7 of this caldef, but the documentation of this being done was just previously omitted being shown in change history version 7 of this caldef.</Description>
    <Author>Ginnard Kimbrough</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
  <CalDefFileChangeRecord>
    <Version>9</Version>
    <Date>05/15/2018</Date>
    <Description>Adding MY21 GB DTC Masks as identified in CR #1820305. The DTC Masks added in this version are DTC_MASK_B13AB_11, DTC_MASK_B13AB_13, DTC_MASK_U160C_00, DTC_MASK_U3000_48,  DTC_MASK_B187F_13, DTC_MASK_B187F_11, DTC_MASK_B186C_13, DTC_MASK_B186C_11 and DTC_MASK_B1236_00</Description>
